text: Birra Stela () is a beer company based in Tirana, Albania. It is the second largest beer producer in the country with an annual production capacity of 250,000 hl, covering roughly 15-18% of the domestic market.Historik i shkurtër"Birra Stela" si një biznes por edhe si një pasuri kombëtare == See also == * Economy of Albania * Companies of Albania * Birra Malto Brewery * Birra Tirana ==References== Category:Beer brands Birra Stela Stela Category:Drink companies of Albania
